link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..50507
Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
program: A332807list(up_to) = { my(v=vector(up_to), p,q); v[1] = 2; v[2] = 3; v[3] = 5; for(n=4,up_to, p = v[n-2]; q = nextprime(1+p); while(q%4 != p%4, q=nextprime(1+q)); v[n] = q); apply(primepi,v); };
xref: Fixed points are given by A000720(A108547(n)), n>=1.
